  .inline-reply-tweetbox {
    background-color: #E8F5FD;
  }

</style>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Jeremy Corbyn Retweeted HuffPost UK</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Since the Tories trebled tuition fees, university bosses pay packets have soared, while staff are fighting for their pensions and students are saddled with 50k+ debt. 

Labour will introduce 20:1 pay ratios in universities and scrap tuition fees to end this scandal.<a href="https://t.co/329fjgt3TG" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/huffpostuk/status/968976379973980160" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/huffpostuk/status/968976379973980160"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/huffpostuk/sta</span><span class="invisible">tus/968976379973980160</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Lecturers will (rightly) do no work while on strike. For me this not only means no classes, but no advice on PhD funding applications which have critical deadlines. Universities need to start taking this seriously and enter meaningful talks with UCU and staff. <a href="/hashtag/ussstrikeessex?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>ussstrikeessex</b></a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Britain has world class universities thanks to the hard work of their staff. They deserve employers that value them and a govt that protects them. Needless attacks on their conditions  and morale will only end up damaging the HE sector which is so vital to our economy and society</p>

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Our university campuses have been brought to the brink of crisis by an intransigent and unreasonable employers body, while the govt has sat on the side lines. Their negotiators should now immediately sit back down for meaningful talks, involving ACAS as an independent mediator.</p>
</div>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Don't ever abuse this day to further your commitment to destroying from within what those brave souls died for. We disagree  that's why were fighting for <a href="/hashtag/votesat16?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>votesat16</b></a>.<a href="https://t.co/yf83Mf8dHw" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/yf83Mf8dHw</a></p>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Jeremy Corbyn Retweeted Theresa May</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">This was a u-turn, after pressure from Labour, on your own policy to attack supported housing. Why did you propose it in the first place?<a href="https://t.co/p4Gy0R7N9k" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/theresa_may/status/923468084664520704" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/theresa_may/status/923468084664520704"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/theresa_may/st</span><span class="invisible">atus/923468084664520704</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">May to freeze tuition fees at 9250 in an attempt to win votes from Labour who will end them: Not a clue Tories.<a href="https://t.co/QzJZhHKQHg" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://www.standard.co.uk/news/politics/theresa-may-pledges-to-freeze-tuition-fees-in-an-overhaul-of-student-funding-a3647716.html" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://www.standard.co.uk/news/politics/theresa-may-pledges-to-freeze-tuition-fees-in-an-overhaul-of-student-funding-a3647716.html"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://www.</span><span class="js-display-url">standard.co.uk/news/politics/</span><span class="invisible">theresa-may-pledges-to-freeze-tuition-fees-in-an-overhaul-of-student-funding-a3647716.html</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">We are proud to be part of the <a href="/JoCoxLoneliness" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="821010896063463426"><s>@</s><b>JoCoxLoneliness</b></a> campaign this month&gt;<a href="https://t.co/dClU0C3nMX" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/sensecharity/status/884334735534772224" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/sensecharity/status/884334735534772224"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/sensecharity/s</span><span class="invisible">tatus/884334735534772224</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Mind added,</p>
  
      <div class="QuoteTweet&#10;    &#10;    &#10;    u-block js-tweet-details-fixer">
  <div class="QuoteTweet-container">

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Exactly a year ago, Jo Cox was killed. Today let's keep her words alive. A powerful way you can help is by sharing Jos words <a href="/hashtag/MoreInCommon?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>MoreInCommon</b></a><a href="https://t.co/rA4rGA26L0" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/rA4rGA26L0</a></p>

  if(window.ttft){
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('page', document.getElementById('swift-page-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('section', document.getElementById('swift-section-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('client_record_time', window.ttft.now());
  }
